  m_text: 'PLANET INFORMATIONS



    Temperature:



    Most of life begins to
    exist in places that are not too cold or too hot, though some people

    prefer
    more harsh and challenging weather and atmosphere conditions, the levels of

    temperature
    are:



    hot



    tempered



    cold




